## Custom editors

Have an editor that's not built-in? Define it in YAML with `mcp_config_path`:

```yaml
custom_editors:
  - name: supermaven
    mcp_config_path: .supermaven/mcp.json

editors:
  supermaven: true  # Don't forget to enable it!
